Rain brought by typhoon Oliwa forced the cancellation of all
the scheduled outdoor matches, and only the four indoor center
court contests were completed.
</P>
<P>
Thailand's Tamarine Tanasugarn overcame a slow start to bounce
back and upset Magdalena Maleeva of Bulgaria 0-6 6-4
6-2. Tanasugarn is to play Seles in the second round. 
</P>
