increase its market share in one of the most dynamic consumer
products countries in the world," said Schwartz.
</P>
<P>
Gao Yuxian, president of the new joint venture and director of
the China Statistical Information and Consulting Center under the
SSB, expressed confidence in the future success of the company.
</P>
<P>
