<HEADLINE> Moroccan Party Congratulates CPC on Congress </HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
<P>
BEIJING, September 16 (Xinhua) -- Morocco's National Assembly
of Independents has sent a congratulatory message to the Communist
Party of China (CPC) on its 15th National Congress.
</P>
<P>
In the telegram to the CPC leadership, President of the
National Assembly of Independents Ahmed Osman said "the 15th
National Congress of the CPC is a congress facing the 21st
century. A friendly, people's China has the ambition to play an
internationally pioneering role in the fields of politics and
economy in the 21st century."
</P>
<P>
The opening-up policy has made contribution to China's economic
development, which enabled China to enjoy an outstanding position
in both Asia and the world, he added.
</P>
<P>
The congress will elect new CPC leadership to dignify the
aspirations of the Chinese people. The National Assembly of
Independents values very much the friendship between the two
parties, he said. 
</P>
