<HEADLINE> Delegates Stress Importance of Party Building (3) </HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
<P>
Currently, the number of Party members who joined the Party
before the founding of new China in 1949 only accounts for a
little over two percent, he said.
</P>
<P>
On the other hand, a large number of young and middled-aged
people have joined the Party. It is estimated that the number of
leading officials of the prefectural level under the age of 40
have exceeded 1,300, while those of the county level also below 40
is approaching 10,000.
</P>
<P>
The participation of young cadres in the leading bodies has
improved the age pattern of the leadership. So far, the
overwhelming majority of those young cadres have proved to be
competent for their jobs.
