<HEADLINE> Mauritian Leader Congratulates CPC on Congress </HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
<P>
BEIJING, September 16 (Xinhua) -- The Republic of Mauritius and
the Mauritius Labor Party has sent a congratulatory message to the
Communist Party of China (CPC) on its 15th National Congress.
</P>
